## Core Rules

- **Code Copying Safety**: Check criticality guide before copying any code
- **Formatting**: No bracketed placeholders in Markdown; prefer backticks/quotes
- **PRD Linkage**: Always include backlog item reference and run validator: `python3 scripts/validate_prd_backlog_linkage.py`
- **Memory**: Use database-based rehydration before reading files directly

